    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you're an ai but i'm just looking for some general info since i can't reach my doctor right now. i've taken ibuprofen in the past and i was always fine. is it generally considered a risky thing for someone with stable CKD, or is it usually okay for just a minor headache?",
